{"tid":421798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「夢見豬」被中國列禁詞　中國男討論遭關7天","createTime":"2017-10-02T14:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T02:01:31.000Z","uid":92301,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3da9e3e65d9d28d0b204682a01d9d942adbf43","tid":421798,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:04:03.000Z","msg":"「夢見豬」近來成為中國網路的新「禁詞」，因為諧音像中共政法委員會書記孟建柱。中國潮州一名男子，近日就因在微信群組中討論「夢見豬」，而被依觸犯公然侮辱罪，遭行政拘留7天。<br />\n<br />\n廣東潮州市公安局湘橋分局19日表示，46歲的田應俊9月16日在一個名為「雅俗共賞」的微信群中，以「夢見豬」影涉中共政法委書記孟建柱，並發佈一系列評論。<br />\n<br />\n田應俊在討論中提到，中國歌手王芳利用和「夢見豬」的關係，排擠他人上春晚；北京市民雷洋因為知道「夢見豬」和王芳及著名主持人楊瀾的關係，所以被國安單位的人「嫖妓死」。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，根據中國法律，田應俊觸犯公然侮辱他人或者捏造事實誹謗他人，可處5天以下拘留或500元人民幣（約2278元台幣）以下罰款；情節較重者，處5天以上10天以下拘留，可以併處500元以下罰款。<br />\n<br />\n目前在微博上搜尋「夢見豬」，已搜不到任何內容，僅出現「根據相關法律法規和政策，『夢見豬』搜尋結果未予顯示」的文字敘述。<br />\n<br />\n滯留美國的中國富商郭文貴日前爆料，中國網路作家周小平的妻子王芳是孟建柱的情人之一，周小平與王芳今年3月的聯姻還是孟建柱安排的。在那之後，有網友因在網路上提到「王芳和孟」而被依「尋釁滋事」拘留。<br />\n<br />\n中國向來禁止民眾以黨和國家領導人名字來開玩笑，除「夢見豬」外，習近平因曾到北京慶豐包子鋪吃包子，而被中國媒體封為「習包子」，但「習包子」一詞隨後也成為網路敏感詞，禁止民眾談論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20171001/1214573/%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A2%E8%A6%8B%E8%B1%AC%E3%80%8D%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%97%E7%A6%81%E8%A9%9E%E3%80%80%E7%94%B7%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E9%81%AD%E9%97%9C7%E5%A4%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20171001%2F1214573%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25A4%25A2%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2588%2597%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%25A9%259E%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%2597%259C7%25E5%25A4%25A9&d=na2eH5RTxquuf%2BfkwpRsd0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=db7048d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20171001/1214573/%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A2%E8%A6%8B%E8%B1%AC%E3%80%8D%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%97%E7%A6%81%E8%A9%9E%E3%80%80%E7%94%B7%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E9%81%AD%E9%97%9C7%E5%A4%A9</a>"},{"pid":"8c308aac784a196d2a5b068f3aca1768b4c66201","tid":421798,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"好名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0912ad766f11aafb84101baedb94fcad6f19263","tid":421798,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:11:01.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街"},{"pid":"324fb466d34e257fbb9cd6be38215c64ccb1e57f","tid":421798,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:15:21.000Z","msg":"wechat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16552de2eb9fe1c74d585d497fdeab1afab12f1","tid":421798,"uid":49588,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:15:52.000Z","msg":"中國文字獄"},{"pid":"ef2cae43137a4ebbd04e43acaffab8430b95c838","tid":421798,"uid":11753,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:19:15.000Z","msg":"中国<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">監控</span>強大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3f7fe584b312d0846af0a39a89c88f79dfd833","tid":421798,"uid":134474,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:55:39.000Z","msg":"睇完都係唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共產嘢我真係唔撚識"},{"pid":"3f4ba6ad26955701d408e94e6f6387d887e97c3d","tid":421798,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"夢見豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 改下花名就又拉又鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都成日比人改花名，有冇得告邢事架"},{"pid":"35b1dabfab27826a58475ae985b6aa73e7439142","tid":421798,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"係咪即係認頭個花朵真係佢本人 <img src=\"/as